  "description": "This table is geared towards words that can be associated with the kinds of actions creatures or villains in a horror adventure may do. This could be used to help describe a crime scene, for instance, where a monster killed a victim. Or, it could be used to help explain an historical event that started a curse, a wicked task that must be completed to perform a ritual, etc.",
